	/Helvetica-Narrow-Oblique
	/NewCenturySchlbk-Roman
	/NewCenturySchlbk-Bold
	/NewCenturySchlbk-Italic
	/NewCenturySchlbk-BoldItalic
	/Palatino-Roman
	/Palatino-Bold
	/Palatino-Italic
	/Palatino-BoldItalic
	/ZapfChancery-MediumItalic
